                            prm.dido_addr_alloc.module_type
                                type of module
                                

1  :INPUT only

2  :OUTPUT only

3  :INPUT and OUTPUT

4  :no INPUT and no OUTPUT

200:out of size for INPUT/OUTPUT

201:violation of PROFIBUS standards

255:unsetting
                                

